## Template 3: Search & Research Prompt

```xml
<research_task>
  <goal>
    [Research question]
  </goal>

  <query_type>
    [ACADEMIC|RECENT_NEWS|CODING|TRANSLATION|...]
  </query_type>

  <format_rules>
    ## Summary
    [2-3 sentence overview]

    ## Key Findings
    [Main points as paragraphs]

    ## Details
    [Supporting details]

    ## Sources
    [Markdown links]
  </format_rules>

  <restrictions>
    - Paraphrase instead of quoting
    - Quote max 15 words per source
    - One quote per source maximum
    - NEVER reproduce song lyrics, poems
    - NEVER cite harmful content
  </restrictions>

  <search_strategy>
    1. [Search query 1]
    2. [Search query 2]
    3. [Optional: deep fetch]
  </search_strategy>

  <output>
    [Formatted response following format_rules]
  </output>

  <personalization>
    [User preferences or "None"]
  </personalization>
</research_task>
```

**Usage**: Research tasks, documentation lookup, architecture analysis
**Source**: Perplexity block XML tags + <citations> pattern

