## Template 5: Simple Q&A / Information Retrieval

```xml
<qa_task>
  <question>
    [User's question]
  </question>

  <context_available>
    [Files/context provided by user]
  </context_available>

  <answer_style>
    <verbosity>[concise|detailed]</verbosity>
    <format>[prose|bullet_points|code|table]</format>
    <include_examples>[yes|no]</include_examples>
  </answer_style>

  <restrictions>
    - Answer directly, no preamble
    - If uncertain, say so
    - If info insufficient, ask clarifying question
  </restrictions>

  <confidence_threshold>
    [High/Medium/Low - adjust response accordingly]
  </confidence_threshold>
</qa_task>
```

**Usage**: Quick questions, information retrieval, explainer tasks
**Source**: Warp.dev section patterns + Claude Sonnet tone rules

